<snippet>
	<content><![CDATA[const truncateString = (str, num) =>
  str.length > num ? str.slice(0, num > 3 ? num - 3 : num) + '...' : str;]]></content>
	<description>Truncates a string up to a specified length.  Determine if the string's `length` is greater than `num`. Return the string truncated to the desired length, with `...` appended to the end or the original string.</description>
	<tabTrigger>truncateString</tabTrigger>
	<scope>source.js</scope>
</snippet>